{"tid":1576412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[等睇唔認同] 穆迪下調港鐵評級展望至負面","createTime":"2019-09-17T08:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T08:53:07.000Z","uid":277339,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee74a56bfa04fb5f47c6cfdfe9a398680be24a82","tid":1576412,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"17.09.2019 16:40<br />\n評級機構穆迪將港鐵(<a href=\"http://00066.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00066.HK&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2Fwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=ec509e4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00066.HK</a>)評級展望，由穩定下調至負面，維持發行人及高級無抵押債券評級為Aa2，主要由於穆迪昨日將香港的評級展望下調為負面。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪指，香港評級展望調整，將會負面影響與政府相關的發行人信貸質素，而港鐵旗下的地鐵公司及九廣鐵路，正是與香港政府有相當大的關聯，對香港評級調整非常敏感。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1173000&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1173000%26csid%3D261_341&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2Fwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=f7464a8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1173000&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"c3cceca090d231a83020e445e6ec6b2a6f047fb1","tid":1576412,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"3dcafe7b14680974a67af6daa8f53daa62ad457b","tid":1576412,"uid":128100,"like":0,"dislike":0,